####################################################################
NOTE: all scripts are unchanged from the training/trial distribution!
#################################################################

The script remove-characters.pl replaces XML entities as given in the BNC with their
ASCII/UTF-8 encoding. 

The script eval.pl copmputes evaluation measures if given a submission file in the correct format and 
a training/testing file as in the *.train/test format with gold standard annotations. 

More on usage is given in the headers of each file.